function_declarations.name: triangle_area_by_sides
function_declarations.description:
Calculates the area of a triangle using Heron's formula.

Args:
    a: Length of the first side.
    b: Length of the second side.
    c: Length of the third side.

Returns:
    The area of the triangle.

parts.text: Find the area of the triangle.

function_declarations.name: isosceles_triangle_perimeter
function_declarations.description:
Calculates the perimeter of an isosceles triangle.

Args:
    base: Length of the base of the triangle.
    side: Length of the equal sides of the triangle.

Returns:
    The perimeter of the triangle.

parts.text: Find the perimeter of the triangle.

function_declarations.name: rectangle_perimeter
function_declarations.description:
Calculates the perimeter of a rectangle.

Args:
    length: Length of the rectangle.
    width: Width of the rectangle.

Returns:
    The perimeter of the rectangle.

parts.text: Calculate the perimeter of the rectangle
